{"image_id": "PNR_2014_page_111", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "Pentair plc and Subsidiaries", "bbox": [162.5, 158.9, 405.1, 179.7]}, {"text": "Notes to consolidated financial statements", "bbox": [162.5, 183.9, 524.0, 204.7]}, {"text": "Fair value of options granted", "bbox": [162.5, 233.9, 408.1, 254.7]}, {"text": "The weighted average grant date fair value of options granted under Pentair plans in 2014, 2013 and 2012 was", "bbox": [162.5, 259.1, 1112.5, 279.9]}, {"text": "estimated to be $23.23, $13.96 and $9.63 per share, respectively. The weighted-average grant date fair value of", "bbox": [162.5, 284.1, 1112.5, 304.9]}, {"text": "options assumed in the Merger was estimated to be $11.76. The total intrinsic value of options that were", "bbox": [162.5, 309.1, 1112.5, 329.9]}, {"text": "exercised during 2014, 2013 and 2012 was $34.8 million, $68.9 million and $41.6 million, respectively. At", "bbox": [162.5, 334.1, 1112.5, 354.9]}, {"text": "December 31, 2014, the total unrecognized compensation cost related to stock options was $5.5 million. This", "bbox": [162.5, 359.1, 1112.5, 379.9]}, {"text": "cost is expected to be recognized over a weighted average period of 1.3 years.", "bbox": [162.5, 384.1, 813.1, 404.9]}, {"text": "We estimated the fair value of each stock option award on the date of grant using a Black-Scholes option pricing", "bbox": [162.5, 431.4, 1112.4, 452.2]}, {"text": "model, modified for dividends and using the following weighted average assumptions:", "bbox": [162.5, 456.4, 885.1, 477.2]}, {"text": "December 31", "bbox": [793.1, 499.3, 909.5, 520.1]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [628.6, 528.4, 670.3, 549.3]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [768.2, 528.4, 809.9, 549.3]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [970.0, 528.4, 1011.7, 549.3]}, {"text": "Granted by", "bbox": [598.2, 557.6, 700.7, 578.4]}, {"text": "Pentair plans", "bbox": [590.1, 578.4, 708.8, 599.3]}, {"text": "Granted by", "bbox": [737.8, 557.6, 840.3, 578.4]}, {"text": "Pentair plans", "bbox": [729.7, 578.4, 848.4, 599.3]}, {"text": "Assumed in", "bbox": [869.3, 557.6, 972.9, 578.4]}, {"text": "Merger", "bbox": [887.5, 578.4, 954.6, 599.3]}, {"text": "Granted by", "bbox": [1001.9, 557.6, 1104.4, 578.4]}, {"text": "Pentair plans", "bbox": [993.8, 578.4, 1112.5, 599.3]}, {"text": "Risk-free interest rate", "bbox": [162.5, 610.9, 343.4, 631.8]}, {"text": "1.44%", "bbox": [672.4, 610.9, 726.2, 631.8]}, {"text": "0.69%", "bbox": [812.0, 610.9, 865.8, 631.8]}, {"text": "0.02 - 0.68%", "bbox": [882.6, 610.9, 990.3, 631.8]}, {"text": "0.96%", "bbox": [1069.8, 610.9, 1123.6, 631.8]}, {"text": "Expected dividend yield", "bbox": [162.5, 634.9, 365.2, 655.7]}, {"text": "1.46%", "bbox": [672.4, 634.9, 726.2, 655.7]}, {"text": "2.01%", "bbox": [812.0, 634.9, 865.8, 655.7]}, {"text": "2.12%", "bbox": [936.5, 634.9, 990.3, 655.7]}, {"text": "2.48%", "bbox": [1069.8, 634.9, 1123.6, 655.7]}, {"text": "Expected share price volatility", "bbox": [162.5, 658.9, 416.8, 679.7]}, {"text": "35.3%", "bbox": [672.4, 658.9, 726.2, 679.7]}, {"text": "36.0%", "bbox": [812.0, 658.9, 865.8, 679.7]}, {"text": "33.0%", "bbox": [936.5, 658.9, 990.3, 679.7]}, {"text": "36.5%", "bbox": [1069.8, 658.9, 1123.6, 679.7]}, {"text": "Expected term (years)", "bbox": [162.5, 682.8, 346.7, 703.7]}, {"text": "5.6", "bbox": [682.8, 682.8, 708.9, 703.7]}, {"text": "5.7", "bbox": [822.4, 682.8, 848.4, 703.7]}, {"text": "0.1 - 5.1", "bbox": [903.4, 682.8, 972.9, 703.7]}, {"text": "5.7", "bbox": [1080.2, 682.8, 1106.3, 703.7]}, {"text": "These estimates require us to make assumptions based on historical results, observance of trends in our share", "bbox": [162.5, 730.1, 1112.4, 750.9]}, {"text": "price, changes in option exercise behavior, future expectations and other relevant factors. If other assumptions", "bbox": [162.5, 755.1, 1112.3, 775.9]}, {"text": "had been used, share-based compensation expense, as calculated and recorded under the accounting guidance,", "bbox": [162.5, 780.1, 1112.4, 800.9]}, {"text": "could have been affected.", "bbox": [162.5, 805.1, 375.5, 825.9]}, {"text": "We based the expected life assumption on historical experience as well as the terms and vesting periods of the", "bbox": [162.5, 852.4, 1112.4, 873.2]}, {"text": "options granted. For purposes of determining expected volatility, we considered a rolling average of historical", "bbox": [162.5, 877.4, 1112.2, 898.2]}, {"text": "volatility measured over a period approximately equal to the expected option term. The risk-free rate for periods", "bbox": [162.5, 902.4, 1112.4, 923.2]}, {"text": "that coincide with the expected life of the options is based on the U.S. Treasury Department yield curve in effect", "bbox": [162.5, 927.4, 1112.3, 948.2]}, {"text": "at the time of grant.", "bbox": [162.5, 952.4, 326.6, 973.2]}, {"text": "Cash received from option exercises for the years ended December 31, 2014, 2013 and 2012 was $46.6 million,", "bbox": [162.5, 999.7, 1112.3, 1020.5]}, {"text": "$102.3 million and $91.6 million, respectively. The actual tax benefit realized for the tax deductions from option", "bbox": [162.5, 1024.7, 1112.4, 1045.5]}, {"text": "exercises totaled $8.3 million, $23.5 million and $12.2 million for the years ended December 31, 2014, 2013 and", "bbox": [162.5, 1049.7, 1112.5, 1070.5]}, {"text": "2012, respectively.", "bbox": [162.5, 1074.7, 320.5, 1095.5]}, {"text": "Restricted stock units", "bbox": [162.5, 1121.8, 345.7, 1142.6]}, {"text": "The following table summarizes restricted stock unit activity under all plans for the year ended December 31,", "bbox": [162.5, 1147.0, 1076.8, 1167.8]}, {"text": "2014:", "bbox": [162.5, 1172.0, 210.0, 1192.8]}, {"text": "Shares in millions", "bbox": [162.5, 1277.4, 313.1, 1298.2]}, {"text": "Number of", "bbox": [902.9, 1256.6, 999.5, 1277.4]}, {"text": "shares", "bbox": [922.8, 1277.4, 979.5, 1298.2]}, {"text": "Weighted", "bbox": [1023.5, 1214.9, 1109.2, 1235.7]}, {"text": "average", "bbox": [1031.7, 1235.7, 1101.1, 12